fields.review: It is a very nice place for couples to eat. It has the one of the best possible coffee in the city
Good Place to eat for students

Zolocrust one of best cafe in Jaipur at present! Only thing is this is really expensive on your pocket!

They serve best thin crust pizza and thinnest out of all I had till now in my life. Hazelnut mousse are also really good!

Whereas salads were as good as any other outlet.

The tastiest Pizza I've ever had. The gorgeously glazed toppings of zucchini mushrooms and everything exquisite make it paradise on thin crust. A little heavy on the pocket, but good to cut down on the bad crowd. It's good to see a bunch of nice people not creating a ruckus unlike other restaurants and relishing their food. The chefs are spot on and super polite in their job, taking in consideration all the needs of the customers. Just a humble request, guests shouldn't shoo and shout at these chefs who are putting in an effort to serve us. Let's be civilized and enjoy our food.
Nice and serene place to eat
Nice and good place for pizza lovers

fields.name: Hotel- Crowne Plaza Jaipur Tonk Road.
fields.location: Sitapura Industrial Area Tonk Road, 302022 Jaipur, India
fields.description:
Get the celebrity treatment with world class service, Offering a spa centre and sauna, Crowne Plaza Jaipur Tonk Road is set in Jaipur in the Rajasthan Region, 5 km from Tonk Road. The hotel has an outdoor pool and fitness centre, and guests can enjoy a drink at the bar.
All rooms come with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. Certain units feature a seating area where you can relax. Extras include slippers, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Crowne Plaza Jaipur Tonk Road features free WiFi throughout the property.
You will find a 24-hour front desk at the property.

fields.name: Treebo Signature Inn
fields.location: E-58, Girdhar Marg, Malviya Nagar, Jaipur, Behind WTP and Behind Fortis hospital
fields.description: Treebo Signature Inn is conveniently situated on the main road in Jaipurs Malviya Nagar. It is just 3 km from the Sanganer Airport and is much preferred for this reason. From the hotel, its easy to get to the corporate offices in the area and also Jaipurs swanky World Trade Park which has a vast array of shopping, dining and leisure options. When you check into the Treebo Signature Inn youll be staying in all-new rooms, done up in an attractive modern style and equipped with all the amenities. All the rooms have ensuite bathrooms and daily housekeeping is available. Theres an in-house roof-top restaurant for when you want to dine in and also facilities for hosting events, a convenience the business traveler looks for. The hotels front desk functions 24/7 and theres a travel desk to assist tourists.

fields.name: Radisson Blu Jaipur
fields.location: 5-6, Airport Plaza, Tonk Road, Durgapura Jaipur -302 018 Rajasthan, India
fields.description: Radisson Blu Jaipur offers its guests a comfortable stay with its multitude of facilities like front desk, daily housekeeping, 24-hour security, free internet access room service, business center, babysitting, parking, 24-hour laundry, express laundry, concierge and travel desk and meeting facilities. The well-equipped board rooms make for an ideal venue to conduct important meetings and conferences. Guests can pamper themselves at health club, outdoor pool and club lounge. Hotel provides lawns and banqueting facility for weddings, parties and other personal events. For dining, guests can relish authentic Indian and world cuisine at Market Place.

fields.name: Novotel Goa Resort and Spa
fields.location: Pinto Waddo, Off Candolim Road, Bardez, Candolim, Goa 403515
fields.description: Along with a marina, this hotel has a full-service spa and a restaurant. Free WiFi in public areas and free valet parking are also provided. Other amenities include an outdoor pool, a health club, and a bar/lounge.

fields.name: Vivanta by Taj Holiday Village
fields.description:
Vivanta by Taj – Holiday Village, Goa is different, yet the same in many ways – it’s one of the best 5-star hotels in Goa. Goa is still the charming village that flirts with the seafront, where fun-lovers come for repeat doses of delight. There's a nice new buzz, however.
In the cottages and villas, the nouvelle restaurants, the island bar and the spa where you'll go, “Ah!” Chef Rego remains, as always, eager to wow you with specially designed meals. Try mixing biz with fun and see how well-wired the village is. 
Soak in one of the best beach resorts in Goa that reflects the spirit of the place. Drive in from the airport delighting in backseat surprises (we won’t reveal what just yet). You might break into a dance at the reception as Goan musicians soulfully strum a guitar and drum a 'ghumot' in a unique Indo-Portuguese style.
And that's just for starters.
